Plot: The sons of police chief Brody must protect civilians at a Sea World theme park after a 35-foot shark becomes trapped in the park with them.
Title: Jaws 3-D
Writer: Peter Benchley (suggested by the novel "Jaws"), Richard Matheson (screenplay), Carl Gottlieb (screenplay), Guerdon Trueblood (story)
Actors: Dennis Quaid, Bess Armstrong, Simon MacCorkindale, Louis Gossett Jr.
